<item>
            <title>[LU-19416] TCU: Rename &quot;.Trash&quot; with &quot;.lustre_trash&quot; to reduce conflict possibilty</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-19416</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Rename &quot;.Trash&quot; with &quot;.lustre_trash&quot; to reduce conflict possibilty as &quot;.Trash&quot; maybe reserved by some systems.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="92491">LU-19416</key>
            <summary>TCU: Rename &quot;.Trash&quot; with &quot;.lustre_trash&quot; to reduce conflict possibilty</summary>
